      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and remains a dependable choice for daily commuting. While the engine and transmission perform reliably, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a small tear on the driver's seat, though all essential electronics and climate controls are fully functional. It is a solid, honest car for someone prioritizing utility over aesthetics.",
