      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in showroom-ready condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved, exhibiting a standard of care synonymous with investment-grade quality. From its flawless exterior finish to its pristine interior appointments, this automobile represents a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising excellence and mechanical integrity.",
