    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that defines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This car has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, appearing as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no imperfections, rock chips, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of wear, and the interior still retains that fresh factory scent. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule exclusively at certified dealerships\u2014full service records are included. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the precision-tuned suspension, operates flawlessly. With curb-rash-free alloy wheels and a spotless engine bay, this car is a rare find suited for a discerning collector or an enthusiast who demands perfection. This is a turnkey opportunity to own a showroom-quality vehicle.",
